@startuml lowtalkers_escape-reality

actor User
participant "React Client" as Client
participant "Express Server" as Server
database "MariaDB" as DB
participant "AWS S3" as S3
participant "Wikipedia API" as Wiki

User -> Client: Access application
Client -> Server: Request authentication
Server -> DB: Verify credentials
DB --> Server: Return user data
Server --> Client: Send authentication response

User -> Client: Explore VR scene
Client -> Server: Request scene data
Server -> DB: Fetch scene information
DB --> Server: Return scene data
Server --> Client: Send scene data
Client -> Client: Render VR scene

User -> Client: Upload 360° image
Client -> Server: Send image data
Server -> S3: Store image
S3 --> Server: Confirm storage
Server -> DB: Save image metadata
DB --> Server: Confirm save
Server --> Client: Confirm upload

User -> Client: Add comment
Client -> Server: Send comment data
Server -> DB: Store comment
DB --> Server: Confirm storage
Server --> Client: Confirm comment added

User -> Client: Like photo
Client -> Server: Send like request
Server -> DB: Update like count
DB --> Server: Confirm update
Server --> Client: Confirm like added

User -> Client: Bookmark Wikipedia article
Client -> Server: Request article info
Server -> Wiki: Fetch article data
Wiki --> Server: Return article data
Server -> DB: Store bookmark
DB --> Server: Confirm storage
Server --> Client: Confirm bookmark added

@enduml